data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home, totaling 1,446 square feet, has been thoughtfully converted to real property and sits on a generous 1.1-acre lot. The property offers ample storage with multiple outbuildings, making it ideal for anyone seeking space for their belongings. Additionally, a separate single-wide manufactured home on the premises can generate extra rental income, enhancing the property's investment potential. While the main residence may benefit from a bit of tender loving care, it boasts great potential for those willing to bring out its inherent charm and value.
